加拿大馬鹿是[[有蹄類|有蹄類]]與[[偶蹄目|偶蹄目]]階層中的大型動物，各足蹄皆擁有雙數的足尖，類似於[[駱駝|駱駝]]、[[山羊|山羊]]與[[牛|牛]]。它同時也是[[反芻動物|反芻動物]]，有著四個胃室，以草、植物、樹葉與樹皮為食。在夏季，加拿大馬鹿幾乎不斷的進食，每日吃進了4至7公斤（10至15磅）的食物<ref name="food">{{cite web | title = Elk Habitat | publisher = Rocky Mountain Elk Foundation | url = http://www.rmef.org/AllAboutElk/ElkHabitat/ | accessdate = 2007-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120908042727/http://www.rmef.org/AllAboutElk/ElkHabitat/ | archive-date = 2012-09-08 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。在北美洲，雄性加拿大馬鹿被稱作「bulls」，雌性的則稱為「cows」。在亞洲，有時則分別以「stag」（雄鹿）與「hind」（母鹿）代替之。

[[File:RooseveltElk_5061t.JPG|thumb]][[紅木國家公園|紅木國家公園]]的一群羅斯福馬鹿。]]
加拿大馬鹿重約[[北美黑尾鹿|北美黑尾鹿]]（mule deer）的二倍，而且有比較紅的毛色，以及暗黃色的臀部大斑點與較小的尾巴。駝鹿比加拿大馬鹿體型大且色澤深，雄鹿有特殊的鹿角，而駝鹿不成群生活。母鹿平均重約225公斤（500磅），到肩部高約1.3公尺（4.5英呎），從鼻到尾長約2公尺（6英呎）。雄鹿發育成熟時體型比母鹿大約大出25%，體重平均重320公斤（700磅），到肩部高約1.5公尺（5英呎），長度平均可到約2.5公尺（8英呎）<ref name="facts">{{cite web | title = Fast Facts | publisher = Rocky Mountain Elk Foundation | url = http://www.rmef.org/AllAboutElk/FastFacts/ | accessdate = 2007-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111123091504/http://www.rmef.org/AllAboutElk/FastFacts | archive-date = 2011-11-23 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。亞種中體型最大的是羅斯福馬鹿，棲息於[[美國|美國]][[加州|加州]]、[[奧勒崗州|奧勒崗州]]與[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]的[[喀斯喀特山脈|喀斯喀特山脈]]西部，以及[[加拿大|加拿大]][[英屬哥倫比亞|英屬哥倫比亞]]省。羅斯福馬鹿曾被再次引入[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]，當地體型最大的雄鹿估計可重達600公斤（1300磅）。<ref name="Alaska">{{cite web |last = Eide |first = Sterling |title = Roosevelt Elk |publisher = Alaska Department of Fish and Game |url = http://www.adfg.state.ak.us/pubs/notebook/biggame/elk.php |accessdate = 2007-06-04 |archive-date = 2007-06-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070605111526/http://www.adfg.state.ak.us/pubs/notebook/biggame/elk.php |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

只有雄鹿才有鹿角，其於春季開始成長，並於每年冬季脫落。最大的鹿角可以達到1.2公尺（4英呎）長，重18公斤（40磅）<ref name="rmef2">{{cite web| title = What Are Elk?| publisher = Rocky Mountain Elk Foundation| url = http://www.rmef.org/AllAboutElk/WhatAreElk/| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120820232110/http://www.rmef.org/AllAboutElk/WhatAreElk| archive-date = 2012-08-20| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。鹿角是以骨頭組成，其可以每日2.5公分（1英吋）的速率成長。鹿角在成長時，會覆蓋上一層有保護作用，柔軟、多血管分布的皮膚，其被稱作[[鹿茸|鹿茸]]。鹿茸會在夏天，鹿角已完全形成後脫落。雄鹿各鹿角上可有八至更多的角叉；然而，角叉的數量和雄鹿的年齡或發育成熟與否並無太大關聯。西伯利亞與北美洲的加拿大馬鹿擁有最大的鹿角，而阿爾泰馬鹿的則最小<ref name="Geist"/>。鹿角的形成與保持是由[[睪丸素|睪丸素]]所控制的<ref name="nwr">{{cite web |last= |first= |title=Friends of the Prairie Learning Center |publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service |url=http://www.tallgrass.org/elks.html |accessdate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101018000502/http://www.tallgrass.org/elks.html |archivedate=2010-10-18 }}</ref>。在晚秋的繁殖季節過後，[[發情期|發情期]]期間環境中[[費洛蒙|費洛蒙]]的分泌減少，而雄鹿的睪丸素分泌也因而下降。睪丸素的減少導致了鹿角的脫落，其通常於早冬時發生。

[[秋季|秋季]]期間，加拿大馬鹿會長出較厚的皮毛，幫助牠們度過寒冬。在西伯利亞和北美洲，加拿大馬鹿的雄鹿、母鹿及小鹿都會長出細頸毛；滿州與賀蘭山馬鹿的母鹿與小鹿則否<ref name="Geist2"/>。到了夏初，厚重的冬季皮毛會脫落，加拿大馬鹿會磨擦樹木或其他物體以除去鹿體上的毛髮。所有的加拿大馬鹿都有清楚、輪廓分明的臀部小斑點及短小的尾巴。牠們視季節與棲息地的種類，會有不同的色澤，毛色在冬季普遍為灰色或其他較淺的顏色，夏季的顏色則較紅、較深。棲息於乾燥氣候區的亞種，比那些棲息於森林中的亞種有毛色較淺的皮毛<ref name="nps">{{cite web| last = Pisarowicz| first = Jim| title = American Elk - Cervus elephus| publisher = National Park Service| url = http://www.nps.gov/archive/wica/Elk.htm| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-date = 2011-04-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110404120422/http://www.nps.gov/archive/wica/Elk.htm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。加拿大馬鹿在夏季時，大部分都是披上淺褐黃色至橙棕色的皮毛，對照著頭部、頸部與腿部的深棕色毛髮。適應於森林的滿州與賀蘭山馬鹿在夏天期間則有較深的紅棕色皮毛，軀幹毛皮與身體其他部位之間毛色的對比較不明顯<ref name="Geist"/>。在許多鹿種中，小鹿普遍在出生時便帶有班點，班點並在夏季結束時消失。發育成熟的滿州馬鹿，則會在夏季毛皮的背部保留少數的橘色斑點，一直到牠們年齡更大時才消失。這些特徵也可以在適應森林的歐洲赤鹿上看見。<ref name="Geist"/>

== 生態學 ==
=== 分布 ===
[[File:Bull_elk_bugling_during_the_fall_mating_season.jpg|thumb]]
現今的亞種是曾經棲息於[[白令陸橋|白令陸橋]]，一種介於亞洲與北美洲之間、於[[更新世|更新世]]連接上述二大陸的[[沙地|沙地]]領域的加拿大馬鹿的後裔。白令陸橋為許多哺乳類物種提供了遷移的途徑，包括[[棕熊|棕熊]]、[[馴鹿|馴鹿]]與駝鹿，以及人類<ref>{{cite book | last =Flannery  | first =Tim | title =The Eternal Frontier: An Ecological History of North America and Its Peoples | url =https://archive.org/details/eternalfrontiere0000flan_m1k4  | publisher = Atlantic Monthly Press | date= 2001-05-10 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/eternalfrontiere0000flan_m1k4/page/212 212]–217 | isbn = 0871137895}}</ref>。當更新世即將告終時，海平面開始上升；加拿大馬鹿南遷至亞洲與北美洲。在北美洲，牠們除了[[凍土層|凍土層]]、沙漠與[[美國墨西哥灣沿岸地區|美國墨西哥灣沿岸地區]]以外，幾乎對整個生態系統都適應良好。[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]南部與[[中亞|中亞]]的加拿大馬鹿曾一度廣泛分布，但如今受到了西列於[[貝加爾湖|貝加爾湖]]的山脈的限制，包括[[蒙古|蒙古]]境內的[[薩彥嶺|薩彥嶺]]與[[阿爾泰山脈|阿爾泰山脈]]，以及臨界於[[吉爾吉斯|吉爾吉斯]]、[[哈薩克|哈薩克]]與中國[[新疆|新疆]]自治區的[[天山|天山]]一帶<ref name="Asia">{{cite web |last= |first= |title=Cervus elaphus |publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature and Natural Resources |url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/41785/all |accessdate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015231800/http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/41785/all |archivedate=2007-10-15 }}</ref>。西伯利亞馬鹿在亞洲的棲息地與北美洲的洛磯山亞種十分相似。

在整個加拿大馬鹿所分布的範圍中，牠們棲息於[[森林|森林]]與林邊棲息地，與其他鹿種相仿。在[[山|山區]]，牠們通常在夏季時生活於較高海拔處，冬季向下遷移。高適應性的加拿大馬鹿也能棲息於北美洲的半沙漠地帶，如[[大盆地|大盆地]]。滿州與賀蘭山馬鹿主要棲息於林間，而牠們尺寸較小的鹿角十分適合山林的環境。

=== 引進 ===
[[File:Wapiti.Nebraska.JPG|thumb]]的圈養範圍中。這些鹿種，最初源自洛磯山鹿群，由於被圈養、受到較少的[[天擇|天擇]]壓力，而呈現出不同的習性。]]
洛杉矶馬鹿亞種被獵人保護組織再次引入美國東部的[[阿帕拉契山|阿帕拉契山區]]一帶，現已滅絕的東歐馬鹿亦曾經棲息與此地<ref name="appalachian">{{cite news| last =Fitzgerald| first =Maria| title =Bears, elk make comeback in E. Ky.| publisher =Appalachian News-Express| year =2007| url =http://www.news-expressky.com/articles/2007/07/15/top_story/01elk.txt| accessdate =2007-07-16| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090828015230/http://www.news-expressky.com/articles/2007/07/15/top_story/01elk.txt| archivedate =2009-08-28}}</ref>。在加拿大馬鹿再次被引進[[美國|美國]]的[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]、[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]與[[田納西州|田納西州]]後，牠們遷移至鄰近的[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]與[[西佛吉尼亞州|西佛吉尼亞州]]，並在當地確立了穩定的族群數<ref name="rmef">{{cite web | last = Ledford | first = David | title = Seeing the Southern Appalachians with 2030 Vision | publisher = Rocky Mountain Elk Foundation | url = http://www.rmef.org/NewsandMedia/PubsTV/Bugle/2005/MarApril/Features/Appalachains.htm | accessdate = 2007-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120219082415/http://www.rmef.org/NewsandMedia/PubsTV/Bugle/2005/MarApril/Features/Appalachains.htm | archive-date = 2012-02-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。加拿大馬鹿也曾被再次引入一些其他的州分，包括[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]、[[密西根州|密西根州]]與[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]。截至1989年，洛磯山亞種的數量估計已達780,500，而北美亞種的估計數量則超過了100萬<ref name="Peek">{{cite web |last=Peek |first=James |title=North American Elk |publisher=U.S. Geological Survey |url=http://biology.usgs.gov/s+t/noframe/c273.htm |accessdate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060927171616/http://biology.usgs.gov/s%2Bt/noframe/c273.htm |archivedate=2006-09-27 }}</ref>。先前歐洲於北美洲的殖民統治時期，北美大陸估計有1000萬的加拿大馬鹿<ref name="facts"/>。加拿大馬鹿在全球的數量，包括人工飼育與野生種，有近200萬。

在牠們的原始棲息地範圍以外，加拿大馬鹿與其他鹿種也被引進了原有少數大型原生有蹄類哺乳動物的區域。為了狩獵、放牧以獲取鹿肉、獸皮與鹿茸而將其引進了這些國家，牠們表現出高度的適應性，有時甚至對當地生態系統產生惡性衝擊與威脅。加拿大馬鹿與馬鹿在二十世紀初被引進了[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]和[[智利|智利]]<ref name="Petersens">{{cite web |last= |first= |title=Elk and Elk Hunting |publisher=Petersen's Hunting |url=http://www.huntingmag.com/big_game/elk_hunting/index1.html |accessdate=2007-06-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060806021213/http://www.huntingmag.com/big_game/elk_hunting/index1.html |archivedate=2006-08-06 }}</ref>。牠們現在在當地被視為[[入侵物種|入侵物種]]，侵犯阿根廷的生態系統，與本土[[智利馬駝鹿|智利馬駝鹿]]等草食動物爭食<ref name="Galende">{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Diet of Huemul deer ( Hippocamelus bisulcus ) in Nahuel Huapi National Park, Argentina| publisher = Taylor and Francis Ltd| url = http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/tandf/snfe/2005/00000040/00000001/art00001| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-date = 2007-09-30| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930181744/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/tandf/snfe/2005/00000040/00000001/art00001| dead-url = no}}</ref>。這些對本土物種所產生的負面影響，導致[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]（IUCN）裁決加拿大馬鹿為世界百大最糟糕的侵略者之一<ref name="invasive">{{cite web| last = Flueck| first = Werner| title = Cervus elaphus (mammal)| work = Global Invasive Species Database| publisher = International Union for Conservation of Nature and Natural Resources| url = http://www.issg.org/database/species/ecology.asp?si=119&fr=1&sts=sss| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-date = 2016-03-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313025333/http://issg.org/database/species/ecology.asp?fr=1&si=119&sts=sss| dead-url = no}}</ref>。加拿大馬鹿與馬鹿也皆曾被引入[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]與[[澳洲|澳洲]]。<ref name="wildlifeinfo">{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Distribution and Movement| work = Cervus elaphus - Red deer (North American Elk)| publisher = Wildlife Information| url = http://www.wildlifeinformation.org/Subdirectories_for_Search2/SampleSpecies/Cervus_elaphus/Cervus_elaphus.html| accessdate = 2007-06-12| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070807125334/http://www.wildlifeinformation.org/Subdirectories_for_Search2/SampleSpecies/Cervus_elaphus/Cervus_elaphus.html| archivedate = 2007-08-07}}</ref><ref name="Corbet">{{cite book| last = Corbet| first = G.B.| coauthors = S. Harris| title = The Handbook of British Mammals | url = https://archive.org/details/handbookofbritis0000unse_t3p5| publisher = Blackwell Science, Inc| year= 1996| isbn = 978-0865427112| oclc = 36133032}}</ref>

鹿種在[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]的引進於十九世紀中葉展開，現今主要的鹿種為歐洲馬鹿，其中加拿大馬鹿僅佔了15%<ref name="farming">{{cite web |last= |first= |title=Deer farming in New Zealand |work= |publisher=Deer Farmer |date=November 29, 2003 |url=http://www.deer-library.com/artman/publish/article_99.shtml |accessdate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524133011/http://www.deer-library.com/artman/publish/article_99.shtml |archivedate=2010-05-24 }}</ref>。這些鹿種已對某些植物物種的森林再生產生了負面衝擊，牠們吃盡了較美味的植物，其後來以那些較不受加拿大馬鹿喜愛的植物來替代。長期的衝擊會對植物類型與自然形成的樹木，以及其他依賴它們的動物與植物物種造成變遷<ref name="Husheer">{{cite journal| last =Husheer| first =Sean W.| title =Introduced red deer reduce tree regeneration in Pureora Forest, central North Island, New Zealand| journal =New Zealand Journal of Ecology| volume =31| issue =1| publisher =New Zealand Ecological Society| date =April 30, 2007| accessdate = 2007-06-04}}</ref>。與智利與阿根廷相同，世界自然保護聯盟已對紐西蘭的馬鹿與加拿大馬鹿鹿種宣告為入侵物種<ref name="invasive"/>。當地並有超過250個個體進行圈養。

== 生物學 ==
=== 繁育與生命週期 ===
[[File:Wapiti_(01)_2006-09-19.JPG|thumb]]
母加拿大馬鹿的[[發情期|發情週期]]相當短暫，只有一至二天，而交配通常包含十二或更多次的嘗試。到了第二年的秋季，母鹿可以誕下一頭或兩頭幼鹿，但誕下兩頭幼鹿的情況較為罕見。普遍來說，母鹿最常在重達至少200公斤（450磅）時繁育<ref name="ndsu">{{cite web |last=Sell |first=Randy |title=Elk |work=Alternative Agriculture Series |publisher=North Dakota State University |url=http://www.ag.ndsu.edu/pubs/alt-ag/elk.htm |accessdate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070510023106/http://www.ag.ndsu.edu/pubs/alt-ag/elk.htm |archivedate=2007-05-10 }}</ref>。[[妊娠|懷孕期]]歷時約240至262天，而幼鹿體重介乎15至16公斤（33至35磅）。當母鹿接近要生產時，牠們會遠離鹿群，保持孤立，直到小鹿夠強壯、能逃離掠食者為止<ref name="birth">{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Elk| work = Living with Wildlife| publisher = Washington Department of Fish and Wildlife| url = http://wdfw.wa.gov/wlm/living/elk.htm| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070702055441/http://wdfw.wa.gov/wlm/living/elk.htm| archive-date = 2007-07-02| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。小鹿和許多鹿種一樣，在產下時便帶有斑點，斑點要到夏末才會消失。滿州馬鹿的夏季皮毛則會在背部留下少數的橘色斑點，直到牠們較成熟後脫落。二周後，小鹿便能夠加入鹿群中，並於二個月時完全斷奶<ref name="adw">{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Cervus elaphus| work = Animal Diversity Web| publisher = University of Michigan, Museum of Zoology| url = http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Cervus_elaphus.html| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-date = 2014-11-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110030425/http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Cervus_elaphus.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。加拿大馬鹿的小鹿在六個月大時體重便相當於一頭成年[[白尾鹿|白尾鹿]]<ref name="wisconsin">{{cite web |last= |first= |title=Elk Biology and interesting facts |work=History of Elk in Wisconsin |publisher=The Wisconsin Elk Reintroduction Project |url=http://www.uwsp.edu/wildlife/elk/biology.htm |accessdate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608213710/http://www.uwsp.edu/wildlife/elk/biology.htm |archivedate=2011-06-08 }}</ref>。剛產下的小鹿會留在母鹿身旁接近一年的時間，在大約下一季的繁育期時離開<ref name="Thomas"/>。所有亞種的懷孕期都是相同的。

加拿大馬鹿在圈養下能活20年甚至更久，但野生的加拿大馬鹿平均壽命只有10至13年。某些較少受到掠食的亞種，其野生的鹿種則平均可以活15年之久。<ref name="smokies">{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Elk| work = Great Smoky Mountains| publisher = National Park Service| url = http://www.nps.gov/grsm/naturescience/elk.htm| accessdate = 2007-06-04| archive-date = 2007-07-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070705013433/http://www.nps.gov/grsm/naturescience/elk.htm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 遷徙 ===
與許多鹿科的鹿種相同，尤其是那些棲息於山區的鹿種，加拿大馬鹿於春季遷移到較高海拔處，隨著積雪退去，再於秋季往反方向移動。狩獵的壓力也影響著遷徙與移居<ref name="migrate">{{cite web| last =Jenkins| first =Kurt| title =Ecology Of Elk Inhabiting Crater Lake National Park And Vicinity| publisher =National Park Service| url =http://www.nps.gov/archive/crla/elk/elk3.htm| date =May 31, 2001| accessdate =2007-06-04| archive-date =2009-08-27| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090827062817/http://www.nps.gov/archive/crla/elk/elk3.htm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。在冬季期間，牠們偏愛林地與隱蔽的山谷便於防風及吃樹皮。羅斯福馬鹿普遍無遷居習慣，因為其食物來源的季節變異性較小。<ref name="Thomas">{{cite book| last = Thomas| first = Jack Ward| coauthors = Dale Toweill| title = Elk of North America, Ecology and Management | publisher = HarperCollins| year= 2002| location = New York| id = ISBN 1-58834-018-X}}</ref>

=== 覓食 ===
[[File:Elk_pellets.jpg|thumb]]
加拿大馬鹿是[[反芻動物|反芻動物]]，而因此擁有四個相隔開的胃。不同於[[白尾鹿|白尾鹿]]與[[駝鹿|駝鹿]]主要是食葉性，加拿大馬鹿和[[牛|牛]]比較相似，其主要是[[草食性|食草性]]，但也與其他鹿類一樣食葉<ref name="Manitoba">{{cite web |title=Feeding Elk Cows |publisher=Manitoba Agriculture, Food and Rural Initiatives |url=http://www.gov.mb.ca/agriculture/livestock/elk/bbb02s03.html |accessdate=2009-01-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611142026/http://www.gov.mb.ca/agriculture/livestock/elk/bbb02s03.html |archivedate=2011-06-11 }}</ref><ref name="Pond">{{cite book| last = Pond| first = Wilson| coauthors = Alan Bell| title = Encyclopedia of Animal Science| publisher = Marcel Dekker| date = November 16, 2005| page = 280| url = http://books.google.com/books?id=1SQl7Ao3mHoC&pg=PA280&lpg=PA280&dq=elk+nutritional+needs&source=web&ots=B7OdOIpr5V&sig=27XJ95emJ5jMnQgUR4zhAzRW7cg&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=9&ct=result| isbn = 0824754964| access-date = 2009-07-16| archive-date = 2014-09-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140928210321/http://books.google.com/books?id=1SQl7Ao3mHoC&pg=PA280&lpg=PA280&dq=elk+nutritional+needs&source=web&ots=B7OdOIpr5V&sig=27XJ95emJ5jMnQgUR4zhAzRW7cg&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=9&ct=result| dead-url = no}}</ref>。加拿大馬鹿主要於早晨與夜晚覓食，期間尋找隱蔽的地區進行消化。牠們的飲食視季節，在天然草葉經一年的補充、樹皮在冬季被吃完，以及[[闊葉草本植物|闊葉草本植物]]與樹木在夏季的成長，而有稍微的變異。加拿大馬鹿每天平均吃掉{{convert|20|lb|kg}}的多種食料<ref name="Feed">{{cite web |title=Elk biology |publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service |date=July 2006 |url=http://www.fws.gov/nationalelkrefuge/Documents/Brochure_ElkBiology.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2009-01-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604154504/http://www.fws.gov/nationalelkrefuge/Documents/Brochure_ElkBiology.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref>，尤其喜愛[[楊樹|楊樹]]嫩枝，其於春季成長。而在某些地域的楊樹樹叢衰退後，棲息於當地的加拿大馬鹿受到了些許衝擊。<ref name="Canada">{{cite web |title=The wolf has a story to tell in Banff National Park |work=Nature |publisher=Envirozine |date=May 31, 2007 |url=http://www.ec.gc.ca/EnviroZine/english/issues/73/nature_e.cfm |acce